&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Clerical Assistant&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a Clerical Assistant to join the Paediatrics Team at Warrington and Halton Teaching Hospitals. We are looking for an enthusiastic and organised individual to support our Medical Secretarial team. Previous experience in a clerical role is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By joining our team you will contribute to the delivery of an outstanding service, with your main responsibilities being to obtain case notes and ensure files are tracked and stored appropriately. You will support the team with general administrative duties such as filing letters, photocopying and handling patient enquiries. You must be a team player, with excellent communication, and able to work under your own initiative.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is for 18 hours.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
